        <p>We believe that the Bible is inspired by God. The Word of God is the single basis of our faith and doctrine
            and leads our actions.</p>

        <p>We believe in the unique God who exists in three distinct identities: the Father, the Son Jesus-Christ and
            the Holy-Spirit.</p>

        <p>We believe that everyone has sinned and fallen short of the glory of God. We believe that sinners are saved
            by grace, through repentance and faith in the perfect and sufficient sacrifice of Jesus at the cross.</p>

        <p>We believe in a Church, not as a human institution but as the gathering of believers around their chief:
            Jesus-Christ.</p>

